The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-19-2013 THURS





The Glenn Beck Program - 09/19/13



Thursday, September 19, 2013 10:38 AM




The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,



Grand Theft Auto 5 is in stores now and Glenn talks about its impact on children.

 Plus, Mark Levin joins the show to talk about his new book,
 The Liberty Amendments.


 Also, the Dairy Queen hero calls and talks about standing up for right and wrong.
